{"tid":1889873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集氣集氣...黑警死全家又叫糊哪.................","createTime":"2020-02-21T00:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T22:06:14.000Z","uid":343821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe16346750737acc7d19b780ce7d3f08850748a8","tid":1889873,"uid":343821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"上次&gt;&gt;&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">柴灣警宿男警一家三口送院</span></span><br />\n食唔出...<br />\n今次...&gt;&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">酒樓出席60人同袍退休宴 防暴警確診 全家有病徵</span></span><br />\n用定藍色配合喪事...大家集氣！<br />\n【本報訊】香港出現首名警務人員確診武漢肺炎。衞生防護中心昨晚公佈，一名居於油塘紀律部隊宿舍的警務人員，昨晚確診新型冠狀病毒，他潛伏期內沒有外遊，據悉駐守北角警署，本月初加入防暴隊服役，18日當天他未有上班，同日出現發燒及咳嗽等病徵，但晚上仍出席一場同袍退休晚宴，同場共有60人參加。跟警員同住的妻子及外母均出現病徵，昨晚送聯合醫院。警方消息稱內部甚為緊張，正全力追查退休晚宴的出席者，以了解有否其他警員出現病徵，甚至要作出隔離。<br />\n記者：陳珏明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ff04be836e14810f4fbed618a7f82ada3b41c1","tid":1889873,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"9 wo😊"},{"pid":"3f8d14777d891ba905d629ce0e51f2ff9114bfad","tid":1889873,"uid":184787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"唔止警謊緊張<br />\n我作為一般小市民都大為緊張<br />\n擔心佢惹唔到比其他狗"},{"pid":"67009e67318fe9b824ed7f9efa59f591999258f1","tid":1889873,"uid":38157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"最怕食詐糊"},{"pid":"240f66850e595662d551209eaae003b86ec1a513","tid":1889873,"uid":343821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T22:06:14.000Z","msg":"又邁進一步哪...<br />\n再多一名飯敍警出現病徵<br />\n【本報訊】48歲高級警員上周四（20日）確診患武漢肺炎，與他一同出席飯局的59位警員均被衞生署列為密切接觸者，須接受檢疫。警方昨日交代檢疫進度，至昨晚僅有30人獲安排入住檢疫中心，包括美孚翠雅山房，撇除三名有病徵需留院治療的警員，其餘26名飯敍集團成員亦去向未明，衞生防護中心主任張竹君稱未清楚安排。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持黃媒...請click入睇下...</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200223/Z4TBXYXTGGGWQCFO536GRDHIGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200223%2FZ4TBXYXTGGGWQCFO536GRDHIGI%2F&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=32b78481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200223%2FZ4TBXYXTGGGWQCFO536GRDHIGI%2F&h=db79adf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200223/Z4TBXYXTGGGWQCFO536GRDHIGI/</a>"}]}